CAPWAP Protected Management Frames (PMF) support

https://github.com/lwfinger/rtl8188eu/issues/20
lower the MTU to around 1000 might help but I don't know why.
USB power saving issue? modprobe 8188eu rtw_power_mgnt=0 modprobe会自动读取 /lib/modules/<kernel-version>/modules.dep 查找依赖

https://github.com/lwfinger/rtl8188eu/commit/67b05876aff0758d787f61e6aa0f55b21ea8e8ad
